data.description: Welcome to 2016 Granite Springs Rd, in the sought-after enclave of Leander, TX. This 4-bedroom residence boasts a grand entryway that leads you to a bright, open-concept living space, a wall of windows that bring in all the natural lighting. The kitchen, designed with the a cook in mind with a large amount of coounter space, including a sprawling island perfect for entertaining. The warm welcoming primary bedroom with double vanity, or step outside to your covered patio with built in grilling area, endless days of relaxation and outdoor gatherings. Just moments from premier shopping, dining, and schools, this home is a harmonious blend of convenience.
